---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Investment Focus | Venera Capital"
	description="Explore Venera Capital's investment sectors and geographic focus across Central Asia."
>

	<!-- ── Page Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
	<section class="page-hero bg-navy">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="section-eyebrow">What We Do</span>
			<h1 style="color:var(--white); font-weight:300; margin-bottom:0;">Investment Focus</h1>
			<hr class="divider" />
			<p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.62); max-width:540px; font-size:1.05rem; line-height:1.85; margin:0;">
				We deploy capital across six core sectors in Central Asia, where the region's structural dynamics create compelling long-term opportunities and where our team has deep expertise.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- ── Sectors ───────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
	<section class="section bg-white">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="section-eyebrow">Our Sectors</span>
			<h2 style="margin-bottom:0;">Where We Invest</h2>
			<hr class="divider" style="margin-bottom:4rem;" />

			<div class="sector-row">
				<div class="sr-icon">
					<svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
						<path d="M20 4L36 13V27L20 36L4 27V13L20 4Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none"/>
						<path d="M20 13V27M13 17.5L27 22.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="sr-content">
					<h3>Energy & Natural Resources</h3>
					<p>Central Asia holds some of the world's largest reserves of oil, natural gas, coal, and strategic minerals. Our energy and resources investments span the full value chain — from upstream extraction to midstream infrastructure and downstream processing. We also actively pursue renewable energy opportunities as the region transitions towards more sustainable energy systems, driven by growing domestic demand and government mandates.</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span class="tag">Oil & Gas</span>
						<span class="tag">Renewables</span>
						<span class="tag">Mining</span>
						<span class="tag">Power Generation</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="sector-row">
				<div class="sr-icon">
					<svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
						<rect x="4" y="10" width="32" height="22" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none"/>
						<path d="M12 21h16M12 27h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						<circle cx="30" cy="13" r="3.5" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="sr-content">
					<h3>Technology & Digital</h3>
					<p>Central Asia's digital economy is growing rapidly, fuelled by high smartphone penetration, improving connectivity infrastructure, and a young, tech-savvy population. We invest in technology companies and digital businesses building the infrastructure and services for this transformation — from e-commerce and fintech to enterprise software and digital payments. We focus particularly on companies with strong network effects and the potential to scale across multiple markets.</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span class="tag">Fintech</span>
						<span class="tag">E-Commerce</span>
						<span class="tag">SaaS</span>
						<span class="tag">Digital Payments</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="sector-row">
				<div class="sr-icon">
					<svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
						<path d="M4 36V18L20 6L36 18V36H26V26H14V36H4Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="sr-content">
					<h3>Real Estate</h3>
					<p>Rapid urbanisation and growing middle-class wealth are driving significant demand for quality real estate across Central Asia's major cities. We invest in residential, commercial, and mixed-use developments, as well as real estate platforms and services businesses. Our focus is on properties and developments that meet the evolving demands of Central Asia's urban populations and growing business communities.</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span class="tag">Commercial</span>
						<span class="tag">Residential</span>
						<span class="tag">Mixed-Use</span>
						<span class="tag">Logistics Real Estate</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="sector-row">
				<div class="sr-icon">
					<svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
						<path d="M4 25C4 25 10 18 20 18C30 18 36 25 36 25" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/>
						<circle cx="20" cy="28" r="5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none"/>
						<path d="M20 7V12"  stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						<path d="M8 12L11 15"  stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						<path d="M32 12L29 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="sr-content">
					<h3>Infrastructure</h3>
					<p>As a critical transit corridor connecting East and West, Central Asia requires substantial investment in transport, logistics, and utility infrastructure. We invest in assets and businesses that build and operate the physical backbone of the regional economy — roads, railways, ports, energy grids, water systems, and logistics hubs. These long-duration investments provide stable returns while contributing to the region's economic development.</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span class="tag">Transport</span>
						<span class="tag">Logistics</span>
						<span class="tag">Utilities</span>
						<span class="tag">Telecoms</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="sector-row">
				<div class="sr-icon">
					<svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
						<rect x="4" y="12" width="32" height="22" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none"/>
						<path d="M12 12V9C12 7.9 12.9 7 14 7H26C27.1 7 28 7.9 28 9V12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none"/>
						<path d="M4 24H36" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/>
						<path d="M16 24V30M24 24V30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="sr-content">
					<h3>Financial Services</h3>
					<p>Central Asia's financial sector remains underpenetrated relative to the region's economic size and growth trajectory. We see significant opportunities in banking, insurance, microfinance, and capital markets across the region. We focus on institutions with strong management, clear competitive positioning, and the ability to grow as financial inclusion deepens and sophisticated financial products become more accessible to businesses and individuals throughout the region.</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span class="tag">Banking</span>
						<span class="tag">Insurance</span>
						<span class="tag">Microfinance</span>
						<span class="tag">Capital Markets</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="sector-row" style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
				<div class="sr-icon">
					<svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
						<path d="M7 34V15L20 6L33 15V34" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none"/>
						<path d="M14 34V25H26V34" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none"/>
						<circle cx="20" cy="17" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="sr-content">
					<h3>Consumer & Retail</h3>
					<p>A young, increasingly affluent, and digitally-connected population is creating a consumer economy of significant scale across Central Asia. We invest in consumer brands, food & beverage businesses, retail chains, and service businesses positioned to serve this growing middle class. We look for businesses with strong brand equity, customer loyalty, and the operational capabilities to expand across the region's major consumer markets.</p>
					<div class="tags">
						<span class="tag">Consumer Brands</span>
						<span class="tag">Food & Beverage</span>
						<span class="tag">Retail</span>
						<span class="tag">Healthcare</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- ── Geographic Focus ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
	<section class="section bg-off-white">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header-centered">
				<span class="section-eyebrow">Geographic Focus</span>
				<h2>Central Asian Markets</h2>
				<hr class="divider divider-center" />
				<p class="section-intro">Our primary investment markets span the five nations of Central Asia, with particular depth in the region's two largest economies.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="markets-grid">
				<div class="market-card market-featured">
					<h4>Kazakhstan</h4>
					<p>Central Asia's largest economy, with a diversified resource base, strong financial infrastructure, and ambitious economic reform agenda. Astana and Almaty are home to the region's most sophisticated business communities.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="market-card market-featured">
					<h4>Uzbekistan</h4>
					<p>The region's most populous country is undergoing one of the most ambitious economic reform programmes in the world, opening new sectors to private investment and foreign capital at a rapid pace.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="market-card">
					<h4>Kyrgyzstan</h4>
					<p>An open economy with a growing services sector, significant mineral resources, and an improving governance framework attractive to foreign investors.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="market-card">
					<h4>Tajikistan</h4>
					<p>Significant hydropower potential and growing trade links are creating new opportunities for patient investors with regional expertise.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="market-card">
					<h4>Broader Region</h4>
					<p>We also evaluate select opportunities in adjacent markets including Azerbaijan and Georgia that connect to our Central Asian investment thesis.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- ── Investment Criteria ───────────────────────────────────── -->
	<section class="section bg-white">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="criteria-grid">
				<div class="criteria-intro">
					<span class="section-eyebrow">Investment Criteria</span>
					<h2>What We Look For</h2>
					<hr class="divider" />
					<p style="color:var(--text-mid);">
						We seek businesses with strong fundamentals, defensible market positions, and significant growth potential within our target sectors and geographies. We welcome both direct approaches and intermediary introductions.
					</p>
					<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">Discuss an Opportunity</a>
				</div>
				<div class="criteria-table">
					<div class="criteria-row">
						<span class="c-label">Investment Size</span>
						<span class="c-value">Flexible — from growth capital to buyouts</span>
					</div>
					<div class="criteria-row">
						<span class="c-label">Stage</span>
						<span class="c-value">Growth-stage and established businesses</span>
					</div>
					<div class="criteria-row">
						<span class="c-label">Structure</span>
						<span class="c-value">Control, co-control, and significant minority positions</span>
					</div>
					<div class="criteria-row">
						<span class="c-label">Holding Period</span>
						<span class="c-value">Typically 4–7 years</span>
					</div>
					<div class="criteria-row">
						<span class="c-label">Sectors</span>
						<span class="c-value">Energy, Technology, Real Estate, Infrastructure, Financial Services, Consumer</span>
					</div>
					<div class="criteria-row">
						<span class="c-label">Geography</span>
						<span class="c-value">Kazakhstan, Uzbekistan, and select Central Asian markets</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>

<style>
	/* Sector rows */
	.sector-row {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
		gap: 2.5rem;
		padding: 3.5rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
		align-items: start;
	}

	.sr-icon { color: var(--gold); padding-top: 0.4rem; }

	.sr-content h3 { font-size: 1.65rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
	.sr-content p  {
		color: var(--text-mid);
		font-size: 0.93rem;
		line-height: 1.78;
		max-width: 680px;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }

	.tag {
		font-size: 0.68rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		color: var(--text-mid);
		background: var(--off-white);
	}

	/* Markets */
	.markets-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5px;
		background: var(--border);
		border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
	}

	.market-card {
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		background: var(--off-white);
		transition: background var(--transition);
	}

	.market-card:hover      { background: var(--white); }
	.market-card.market-featured { background: var(--white); }

	.market-card h4 {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--navy);
	}

	.market-card p {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: var(--text-mid);
		line-height: 1.65;
		margin: 0;
	}

	/* Criteria */
	.criteria-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
		gap: 5rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.criteria-table {
		border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
		padding-left: 4rem;
	}

	.criteria-row {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: baseline;
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 1.15rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.criteria-row:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }

	.c-label {
		font-size: 0.68rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		flex-shrink: 0;
		width: 130px;
	}

	.c-value {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		text-align: right;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.sector-row      { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; }
		.sr-icon         { display: none; }
		.markets-grid    { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
		.criteria-grid   { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
		.criteria-table  { border-left: none; padding-left: 0; }
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.markets-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.criteria-row { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; }
		.c-value      { text-align: left; }
	}
</style>
